---
import LoanProductLayout from "@/layouts/LoanProductLayout.astro";
const title = "Merchant Cash Advance";
const subtitle = "Flexible funding based on card sales. A merchant cash advance lets you unlock funding repaid as a fixed percentage of your card sales—so repayments flex with revenue.";
---
<LoanProductLayout title={title} subtitle={subtitle} updatedAt="November 2025">
  
  <!-- What is a merchant cash advance -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">What is a merchant cash advance?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      A merchant cash advance is a type of unsecured funding based on your business's average monthly card sales. It allows you to borrow a lump sum upfront and repay it gradually through a fixed percentage of each card transaction until the balance is cleared.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      There are no fixed monthly repayments. You repay more when business is booming, and less during slower periods. This makes it ideal for businesses with fluctuating income, such as retail, hospitality, beauty, or tourism.
    </p>
    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-lime-200 bg-lime-50 mt-6">
      <p class="text-neutral-800">
        <strong class="text-black">Key feature:</strong> Repayments automatically adjust to your card sales volume, so you never have to worry about fixed monthly payments during quiet periods.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">How does it work?</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Apply based on card takings</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Apply based on your average monthly card takings and business history.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Get approved and funded</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Get approved and receive a lump sum (typically €2,000 to €300,000).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Repay through card sales</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Repay through an agreed percentage of daily or weekly card sales.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">4</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">No fixed terms</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">No fixed terms - you repay as you trade, automatically.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Example</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-3">
        If you take €20,000 in monthly card payments and the provider advances you €15,000, you'll repay through a fixed percentage of your future card sales - say 10%.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        This means if one day you make €1,000 in card sales, €100 goes toward repayment. If the next day you make €400, you repay €40. Your repayments automatically adjust to your daily revenue.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Common use cases -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Common use cases</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Managing seasonal cash flow</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Perfect for hospitality, retail, beauty, or tourism businesses that experience busy and quiet periods throughout the year.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Investing in stock or inventory</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Buy more stock ahead of peak trading periods without tying up cash flow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Covering unexpected costs</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Pay for repairs, emergency staffing, or last-minute supplier expenses with minimal disruption.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Upgrading premises or equipment</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Refurbish your shop, update your salon equipment, or invest in tools to grow your business.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Launching a campaign</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Boost visibility and sales by investing in digital marketing or local promotions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Expanding operations</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Open new locations, hire additional staff, or invest in growth initiatives during peak seasons.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Is it right for your business -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Is MCA right for your business?</h2>
    
    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50 mb-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Merchant cash advances are best suited for:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Businesses with regular card sales (retail, hospitality, beauty, and service industries)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">SMEs needing flexible, fast, and unsecured finance</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Businesses with fluctuating income patterns</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Companies trading through a card terminal or online payment gateway</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-neutral-700">Businesses needing quick access to funding without providing collateral</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        It may not be suitable for B2B businesses with high invoice volumes and few card transactions. If you mainly invoice customers, invoice finance may be a better fit.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        MCAs are also less ideal for businesses with very low card sales volumes or those needing long-term investment capital.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MCA vs business loan -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Merchant cash advance vs business loan</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-200">
            <th class="text-left py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-black">Feature</th>
            <th class="text-left py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-black">Merchant Cash Advance</th>
            <th class="text-left py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-black">Business Loan</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Repayment</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">% of card sales</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Fixed monthly repayments</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Suitable for</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Seasonal income businesses</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Predictable cash flow</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Collateral required</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">No</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Sometimes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Flexibility</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">High</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Medium</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-neutral-100">
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Application speed</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Fast (24–72 hours)</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Medium (a few days to weeks)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Best for</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Fluctuating revenue</td>
            <td class="py-4 px-4 text-neutral-700">Stable income</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What lenders look at -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">What lenders look at</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Lenders typically review several key factors when evaluating merchant cash advance applications:
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-black">Average monthly card revenue</strong> – usually €2,000 minimum, though requirements vary by provider</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-black">Trading history</strong> – usually 6–12 months of consistent card sales</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-black">Volume and consistency</strong> – regular, consistent card transactions show stable revenue</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-black">Business type and sector</strong> – risk profile of your industry and business model</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-black">Overall credit health</strong> – personal or business credit scores, though less critical than card sales</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50 mt-6">
      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">
        <strong class="text-black">Good news:</strong> You don't usually need a business plan or security to apply. Approval is often based more on your card sales record than credit score.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Eligibility and requirements -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">Eligibility and requirements</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      To qualify for an MCA, lenders typically expect:
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Trading history</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">At least 3–6 months of card sales history with consistent transactions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Minimum turnover</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">A minimum monthly turnover (often €2,500–€5,000 in card sales).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Card terminal</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Trading through a card terminal or online payment gateway.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Actively trading</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Actively trading business with regular card transactions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50 mt-6">
      <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">
        Credit checks may still apply, but approval is often based more on your card sales record than credit score. This makes MCAs accessible to businesses with less-than-perfect credit.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Example scenario -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">Example scenario</h2>
    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50">
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        A café with average monthly card takings of €15,000 applies for an MCA. The lender advances €20,000 with repayments set at 10% of daily card sales.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        If the café has a busy day with €1,500 in card sales, it repays €150. On quieter days with €500 in sales, repayments are only €50.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        This helps the café manage cash flow without worrying about fixed repayments during slower weeks. The advance is automatically repaid as the business trades, with no fixed monthly commitment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Pros and considerations -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Pros and things to consider</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Pros</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Repayments flex with your income automatically</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">No fixed monthly instalments</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Quick access to funding (often 24–72 hours)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">No need for assets as collateral</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Simple application based on card takings</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Less emphasis on credit score than traditional loans</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Things to consider</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
